    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is an absolute dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it\u2014always kept in the garage and pampered every step of the way. The paint is sparkling, the interior is spotless, and it drives so smoothly. It\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag! I\u2019m so excited for someone to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
