      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the high-revving S65 V8 era, this E92 M3 is in absolute mint condition. The naturally aspirated 4.0L powerplant features synchronized individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings have been addressed proactively, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides sharp, adaptive damping without compromise. The chassis remains rigid with zero bushing fatigue, ensuring optimal lateral kinematics. This is a collector-grade specimen with flawless paint depth and a cockpit that retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
